# [[harsh|Harsh]], [[piercing]] or [[stinging]].
#* '''1999''', {{w|Neil Gaiman}}, ''Stardust'', p.31 (Perennial paperback edition)
#*: It was at the end of February,{{...}}when the world was cold, and a '''bitter''' wind howled down the moors{{nb...}}.
